snippet.textDisplay:
Lyrics by Faiz sahab....singer... Malika e TARANNUM...madam Noorjehan ji....film Qaidi 1964.... picturised on Shamim ara.. legendary Pakistani actress.....
      Noorjehan ji was in Kolkata about 8 years...and in Mumbai ..10 years...after partition Noorjehan ji left India...
  Faiz Ahmed sahab was born in narowal..punjab..now in Pakistan...
   Shamim ara...she was born in Aligarh.. Uttar Pradesh....she too left India....
   But these people are cultural heritage bridge between India and Pakistan......
       Divided physically...but United by hearts...
      Pakistani PM said ...KASHMIR KE BINA PAKISTAN ADHURA H....Indian PM said... PAKISTAN KE BINA HINDUSTAN ADHURA HAI.....
     Noorjehan ji......jaha be ho aap.... undivided India ki khubsurat pal aap ke saath hi tha...
